{
  "stem": "6258.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my diary is the only existing document who came out of the ghetto in Krakow, in Polish language, from the milieu of Polish Jewish intelligentsia.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is no other written there with dates, with everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This books?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- that diary was published by Polish Cultural Foundation in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it was not published by the Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when I sent-- transcribed this diary and I sent it to Yad Vashem, later on it was sent to a competition of Jews from Krakow in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because this is the only document, well, not written in retrospect-- like was written about 40 years later in retrospect from the memories of the people who were there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my diary was really written there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this diary got an award on this competition there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that introduction to this diary was written by Gideon Hausner, who was the prosecutor of-- of Eichmann in Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then it was supposed to be published there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they did not have money here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was also, well, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But anyway, the Polish Cultural Foundation found out about this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they wanted to publish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they published it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They published this, I think, 1987.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's out of print.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this books has-- well, maybe I-- I still have this main book of my diary with cover, which I make sketch, my drawings about it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I hope.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was that motto that I choose for my diary, that if evil will try to get to me, lift your spirits so high that it could not reach you.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Zaleski.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A romantic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't even remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just know Zaleski.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, Polish romantic poet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
